    <h2>🔍 Australian Carer Research Highlights</h2>
    <ul class="resource-links">
      <li><a href="https://engage.dss.gov.au/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Stage-1-rapid-scoping-review.pdf">National Carer Strategy Evidence Base</a> – Rapid review from AIFS</li>
